---
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
import { getCollection } from "astro:content";
import Heading, { HeadingType } from "@components/Heading.astro";
import Paragraph, { ParagraphStyle } from "@components/Paragraph.astro";
import ContentPageLayout from "src/layouts/ContentPageLayout.astro";
const boardMembers = await getCollection("board-members");
---

<ContentPageLayout title="About Us">
    <Heading type={HeadingType.H1}>About Friends of Donegal</Heading>

    <Heading type={HeadingType.H2}>Mission</Heading>
    <Paragraph>
        We harness the collective power and influence of the community to improve the lives of our
        neighbors.
    </Paragraph>

    <Heading type={HeadingType.H2}>Vision</Heading>
    <Paragraph>Together we promote hope and equity for all.</Paragraph>

    <Heading type={HeadingType.H2}>Core Values</Heading>

    <Heading type={HeadingType.H3}>Equity</Heading>
    <Paragraph>
        We believe everyone should be seen, heard, valued, and empowered to succeed. We work to
        change practices, structures, and policies to realize equity for everyone.
    </Paragraph>

    <Heading type={HeadingType.H3}>Making Sustainable Change</Heading>
    <Paragraph>
        We are committed to the economic security of all people. Unlike systems that create and
        maintain disparities, we adopt approaches that meet the individual's needs the way they
        experience social problems.
    </Paragraph>

    <Heading type={HeadingType.H3}>Persistent</Heading>
    <Paragraph>
        We understand to make sustainable change we must pursue our goals even when it is difficult
        or opposed by others. We are driven to think and do what is best for those in need in our
        community.
    </Paragraph>

    <Heading type={HeadingType.H3}>Opportunity</Heading>
    <Paragraph>
        We work with others to create the circumstances for members of our community to thrive.
    </Paragraph>

    <Heading type={HeadingType.H3}>With</Heading>
    <Paragraph>We are here to walk with you, team with you and celebrate with you.</Paragraph>

    <Heading type={HeadingType.H3}>Empathy</Heading>
    <Paragraph>
        We are genuinely interested in the emotional state of others and engage with those emotions
        to compassionately take action.
    </Paragraph>

    <Heading type={HeadingType.H3}>Relationships</Heading>
    <Paragraph>
        RelationshipsWe build connections between people and organizations, founded in mutual
        respect, to work together to bring about change.
    </Paragraph>

    <Heading type={HeadingType.H2}>Our Board of Directors</Heading>
    {
        boardMembers.map((member) => (
            <>
                <Heading type={HeadingType.H3}>
                    {member.data.name}
                    {member.data.title && ` - ${member.data.title}`}
                </Heading>
                <Paragraph style={ParagraphStyle.Spaced}>
                    <Image
                        src={member.data.imageUrl}
                        width={300}
                        height={400}
                        alt={`Image of ${member.data.name}, ${member.data.title}`}
                    />
                    {member.body}
                </Paragraph>
            </>
        ))
    }

    <Heading type={HeadingType.H2} id="501c3">501C3 Information</Heading>
    <Paragraph>
        Friends of Donegal (FOD) is a 501(c) (3) organization. The official registration and
        financial information of FOD may be obtained from the Pennsylvania Department of State by
        calling toll free within PA. 1-800-732-0999. Registration does not imply endorsement.
    </Paragraph>
</ContentPageLayout>
